  "The constant term of the dividend when evaluated systematically": "系统地评估红利的固定期限",
  "The remainder is what is left after dividing. When dividing by a linear factor, the remainder is a constant. If the remainder is 0, the divisor is a factor of the dividend.": "剩余部分是分割后留下的。 当用线性系数除以时, 剩余部分是一个常数。 如果剩余部分为 0, 则三分位数是红利的一个系数 。",
