  "Polynomial long division follows the same process as long division of numbers: divide, multiply, subtract, bring down. It works with any polynomial divisor.": "多元长的分隔符遵循与数字的长分割法相同的过程: 分隔、 乘、 减、 调低。 它与任何多元断裂符一起工作 。",
