  "What is the division algorithm for polynomials?": "多面体的分裂算法是什么?",
  "f(x) = d(x) * q(x) + r(x), where the degree of r is less than the degree of d": "(fx) = d(x) * q(x) + r(x) + r(x),当 r 度小于 d 度时",
