  "f(x) = d(x) + q(x) + r(x) according to conventional analysis": "根据常规分析,(fx) = d(x) + q(x) + r(x) + r(x) = d(x) + q(x) + r(x)",
  "f(x) = d(x) * q(x), particularly regarding divisor in the": "(f)(x) = d(x) * q(x) ,特别是其中的divisor",
  "The division algorithm states that dividend = divisor * quotient + remainder, where the remainder's degree is strictly less than the divisor's degree.": "分法算法指出,股息=divisor * 商数 + 剩余部分,其余部分的学位严格低于divisor的学位。",
  "What does it mean if the remainder of polynomial division is zero?": "如果多边分裂的剩余部分是零,那是什么意思?",
