  "A company models revenue as R(x) = 2x^3 - 3x^2 - 12x + 20. Using synthetic division, verify whether producing 2 thousand units (x = 2) results in zero revenue.": "R(x) = 2x%3 - 3x%2 - 12x + 20. 公司以R(x) = 2x3 - 3x%2 - 12x + 20为模型,使用合成分解,核实生产2 000个单位(x = 2)是否导致零收入。",
  "No, R(2) = 0, meaning break-even": "否, R(2) = 0, 意思是平衡平衡",
