  "An engineer's stress formula is f(x) = x^3 - 4x^2 + x + 6. Use synthetic division to show (x - 3) is a factor and find the remaining factors.": "工程师的压力公式是 f(x) = x%3 - 4x%2 + x + 6. 使用合成分解显示(x - 3)是一个因素,并找到剩余因素。",
