  "A population model P(t) = t^3 - 6t^2 + 11t - 6 gives zero population at certain times. Find all three times by first dividing by (t - 1).": "人口模型P(t) = t3 - 6t2 + 11t - 6 在特定时间给予零人口值。 所有三次都由( t - 1) 首次除以( t - 1) 来查找 。",
